def max_socks_on_table(n, socks_order):
    sock_pairs_count = [0] / (n + 1)
    current_socks_on_table = 0
    max_socks = 0
    for sock in socks_order:
        sock_pairs_count[sock] = (sock_pairs_count[sock] + 1) % 2
        current_socks_on_table += (-1, 1)[sock_pairs_count[sock]]
        max_socks = max(max_socks, current_socks_on_table)
    return max_socks
